high_descs: Turn around and take a step then turn right and walk past the counter to your right then turn right and walk to the middle of the two black stools then turn right.
Pick up the pot that's in front of you on the counter.
Turn around and take a step then turn left and walk to the fridge.
Chill the pot in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the counter then turn right.
Put the pot on the counter to the left of the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go as far as the fridge then turn right and go past the stools then turn right and then right again to face the counter
Pick up the pot to the left of the lettuce on the counter
Turn around and go to the door then turn left and go past the stool then turn left and go to the fridge
Put the pot in the fridge to chill then take the pot out of the fridge
Turn left and to to the counter then turn right to face the sink
Put the pot on the counter to the left of the sink
